Triangle Microwave Inc saidit is involved in talks on its possible purchase by a"substantial U.S. company" it did not identify.    Triangle said no agreement has yet been reached and therecan be no assurance that one will be reached. Any acquisitioonwould be subject to approval by its shareholders and toregulatory filings, it said.    Triangle Microwave makes microwave system components andhad earnings for the first half ended January 31 of 1,055,000dlrs on sales of 7,292,000 dlrs, up from earnings of 763,000dlrs on sales of 6,034,000 dlrs a year before. Reuter&#3;